Motech Industries to Form Venture With Green Energy, Taiwan Poly-Silicon

-- B y   Y u - H u a y   S u n
-- 
2011-03-14T08:59:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/motech-industries-to-form-venture-with-green-energy-taiwan-poly-silicon.html
  Motech Industries Inc. (6244)  will form a
venture with  Green Energy Technology Inc. (3519)  and Taiwan Poly-
Silicon Corp. to produce polysilicon wafers, Motech said in a
statement to the stock exchange today.  The venture, to have an initial capital of NT$1 billion,
will be 30 percent owned by Motech, 40 percent by Green Energy
and 30 percent by Taiwan Poly-Silicon, according to the
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yu-Huay Sun in Taipei at 
 ysun7@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ryan Woo at 
 rwoo5@bloomberg.net  